---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="La Brigade Mobile | Réparation Expert & Reconditionné Certifié">
    <main>
        <!-- HERO SECTION -->
        <section class="hero-section">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1597872200969-2b65d56bd16b?q=80&w=1920" alt="Reparation Tech" class="hero-bg">
            <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
            <div class="container hero-content fade-in-up">
                <div style="display:inline-block; background:var(--color-primary); color:white; padding:0.4rem 1rem; border-radius:20px; font-size:0.8rem; font-weight:bold; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; margin-bottom:1rem;">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-small">verified</span> N°1 de la réparation à Toulouse
                </div>
                <h1 class="hero-title">Écran cassé ?<br>On répare en 30 min.</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">Smartphone, tablette ou PC : diagnostic gratuit, prix fixe, garantie 12 mois. Plus de 15 000 appareils réparés.</p>
                <div class="hero-actions">
                    <a href="/devis" class="btn-primary" style="font-size:1.1rem; padding:1rem 2rem;">Devis gratuit en 2 min</a>
                    <a href="tel:0756916593" class="btn-secondary" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color:white; border-color:white; font-size:1.1rem; padding:1rem 2rem;"><span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-small">call</span> 07 56 91 65 93</a>
                </div>
                <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; margin-top:2rem; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:center;" class="mobile-stack">
                    <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size:0.9rem;">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:var(--color-primary);">speed</span> 30 min en moyenne
                    </div>
                    <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size:0.9rem;">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:var(--color-primary);">workspace_premium</span> Garantie 12 mois
                    </div>
                    <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size:0.9rem;">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:var(--color-primary);">thumb_up</span> 4.9/5 avis clients
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SCROLLING BANNER -->
        <div class="scrolling-banner">
            <div class="scrolling-content">
                <span><span class="material-symbols-outlined">build</span> Réparation express 30 min</span>
                <span><span class="material-symbols-outlined">verified</span> Pièces haute qualité</span>
                <span><span class="material-symbols-outlined">history</span> Devis gratuit immédiat</span>
                <span><span class="material-symbols-outlined">verified_user</span> Garantie 12 mois</span>
                <span><span class="material-symbols-outlined">location_on</span> Atelier local (Toulouse)</span>
                <span><span class="material-symbols-outlined">build</span> Réparation express 30 min</span>
                <span><span class="material-symbols-outlined">verified</span> Pièces haute qualité</span>
                <span><span class="material-symbols-outlined">history</span> Devis gratuit immédiat</span>
                <span><span class="material-symbols-outlined">verified_user</span> Garantie 12 mois</span>
                <span><span class="material-symbols-outlined">location_on</span> Atelier local (Toulouse)</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- TARIFS REPARATION POPULAIRES -->
        <section class="section-padding" style="background:var(--color-white);">
            <div class="container">
                <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:3rem;">
                    <p style="text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px; font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--color-primary); font-weight:bold; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Tarifs Transparents</p>
                    <h2 class="section-title fade-in-up" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Nos Réparations les Plus Demandées</h2>
                    <p style="color:#666; max-width:600px; margin:0 auto;">Prix fixes, pas de surprise. Diagnostic offert, pièces premium incluses.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap:1.5rem;">
                    <div class="fade-in-up" style="transition-delay:0.1s; background:white; border:2px solid #f0f0f0; border-radius:12px; padding:2rem; text-align:center; transition:border-color 0.3s;">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:2.5rem; color:var(--color-primary); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">phone_android</span>
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Écran iPhone</h3>
                        <p style="color:#666; font-size:0.85rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">iPhone 11 à 15 Pro Max — pièce + pose</p>
                        <div style="font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--color-dark); margin-bottom:0.25rem;">à partir de 69€</div>
                        <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Réparé en 20 min sur place</p>
                        <a href="/devis" class="btn-primary" style="width:100%;">Obtenir un devis</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fade-in-up" style="transition-delay:0.2s; background:var(--color-dark); border:2px solid var(--color-primary); border-radius:12px; padding:2rem; text-align:center; color:white; position:relative;">
                        <div style="position:absolute; top:-12px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); background:var(--color-primary); color:white; padding:0.25rem 1rem; border-radius:20px; font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:bold; text-transform:uppercase;">Le + demandé</div>
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:2.5rem; color:var(--color-primary); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">battery_charging_full</span>
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; color:white;">Batterie Smartphone</h3>
                        <p style="color:#aaa; font-size:0.85rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">iPhone & Samsung — batterie premium</p>
                        <div style="font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">à partir de 49€</div>
                        <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#888; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Réparé en 15 min sur place</p>
                        <a href="/devis" class="btn-primary" style="width:100%;">Obtenir un devis</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fade-in-up" style="transition-delay:0.3s; background:white; border:2px solid #f0f0f0; border-radius:12px; padding:2rem; text-align:center; transition:border-color 0.3s;">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:2.5rem; color:var(--color-primary); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">power</span>
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Connecteur de Charge</h3>
                        <p style="color:#666; font-size:0.85rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Tous smartphones — micro-soudure incluse</p>
                        <div style="font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--color-dark); margin-bottom:0.25rem;">à partir de 59€</div>
                        <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Réparé en 30 min sur place</p>
                        <a href="/devis" class="btn-primary" style="width:100%;">Obtenir un devis</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align:center; margin-top:2rem;">
                    <a href="/reparation" style="color:var(--color-primary); font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem;">
                        Voir tous nos tarifs de réparation <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- COMMENT CA MARCHE -->
        <section class="section-padding">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title fade-in-up">Votre Réparation en 4 Étapes</h2>
                <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap:2rem; text-align:center;">
                    <div class="fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:3rem; color:var(--color-primary);">manage_search</span>
                        <h3 style="margin:1rem 0;">1. Diagnostic</h3>
                        <p style="color:#666; font-size:0.9rem;">Analyse complète et gratuite du problème par nos experts.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:3rem; color:var(--color-primary);">history</span>
                        <h3 style="margin:1rem 0;">2. Devis</h3>
                        <p style="color:#666; font-size:0.9rem;">Prix fixe et transparent annoncé avant toute intervention.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.3s;">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:3rem; color:var(--color-primary);">build</span>
                        <h3 style="margin:1rem 0;">3. Réparation</h3>
                        <p style="color:#666; font-size:0.9rem;">Intervention rapide avec des pièces premium sélectionnées.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.4s;">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:3rem; color:var(--color-primary);">verified</span>
                        <h3 style="margin:1rem 0;">4. Garantie</h3>
                        <p style="color:#666; font-size:0.9rem;">Votre appareil est testé et garanti pendant 1 an.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CATEGORIES -->
        <section class="section-padding" style="background:var(--color-white);">
            <div class="container">
                <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
                    <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Expertise Technique</p>
                    <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Nos Services de Réparation</h2>
                    <p style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; color: #666;">Spécialistes de la micro-soudure et de la remise en état express. Nous redonnons vie à vos appareils là où d'autres abandonnent.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="categories-grid">
                    <a href="/reparation" class="category-card fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.1s; border: 2px solid var(--color-primary); grid-column: span 2;">
                        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; height: 100%;">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1597872200969-2b65d56bd16b?q=80&w=600" alt="Atelier Réparation" class="category-img" style="height: 100%; object-fit: cover;">
                            <div class="category-content" style="text-align: left; padding: 2.5rem;">
                                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-primary);">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">verified</span>
                                    <span style="font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.8rem;">Expertise Certifiée</span>
                                </div>
                                <h3 class="category-title" style="font-size: 2.5rem;">Réparation Atelier Express</h3>
                                <p class="category-desc" style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Écrans, batteries, connecteurs et micro-soudure. Diagnostic gratuit et réparation en 30 minutes dans 90% des cas.</p>
                                <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
                                    <span class="btn-primary" style="padding:0.75rem 1.5rem;">Prendre RDV</span>
                                    <span class="btn-secondary" style="padding:0.75rem 1.5rem;">Consulter les prix</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/devis?cat=micro-soudure" class="category-card fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550751827-4bd374c3f58b?q=80&w=600" alt="Micro-soudure" class="category-img">
                        <div class="category-content">
                            <h3 class="category-title">Micro-Soudure</h3>
                            <p class="category-desc">Réparation de carte mère et récupération de données complexes.</p>
                            <span class="catalog-link">Expertise Pointue <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/devis?cat=deoxydation" class="category-card fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.3s;">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1592899677977-9c10ca588bbd?q=80&w=600" alt="Désoxydation" class="category-img">
                        <div class="category-content">
                            <h3 class="category-title">Désoxydation</h3>
                            <p class="category-desc">Sauvetage d'appareils tombés dans l'eau. Traitement ultrason.</p>
                            <span class="catalog-link">Agir vite <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-top: 4rem; text-align: center;">
                    <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-title); font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Besoin d'un nouvel appareil ?</h3>
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                        <a href="/smartphones" class="btn-secondary" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; border-color: #DDD; font-size: 0.9rem;">Smartphones Reconditionnés</a>
                        <a href="/ordinateurs" class="btn-secondary" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; border-color: #DDD; font-size: 0.9rem;">PC & Mac Occasion</a>
                        <a href="/tablettes" class="btn-secondary" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; border-color: #DDD; font-size: 0.9rem;">Tablettes Garanties</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- BANDEAU URGENCE REPARATION -->
        <section style="background:var(--color-primary); padding:2rem 0;">
            <div class="container" style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:1.5rem;" class="mobile-center">
                <div style="color:white; text-align:inherit;">
                    <h3 style="font-size:1.5rem; margin-bottom:0.25rem; color:white;">Urgence réparation ?</h3>
                    <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">Sans rendez-vous, diagnostic immédiat et gratuit en boutique.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:center;">
                    <a href="tel:0756916593" style="background:white; color:var(--color-primary); padding:0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius:8px; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem;"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">call</span> Appeler maintenant</a>
                    <a href="/devis" style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0.2); color:white; padding:0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius:8px; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">description</span> Devis en ligne</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ENGAGEMENT -->
        <section class="section-padding">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title fade-in-up">L'Engagement Réparation</h2>
                <div class="features-grid">
                    <div class="fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
                        <span class="feature-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">verified_user</span></span>
                        <h3 class="feature-title">Savoir-faire Expert</h3>
                        <p>Plus de 10 ans d'expérience dans la micro-soudure et la réparation high-tech de précision.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                        <span class="feature-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">history</span></span>
                        <h3 class="feature-title">Rapidité Incroyable</h3>
                        <p>90% des réparations (écrans, batteries) sont effectuées en moins de 30 minutes sur place.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.3s;">
                        <span class="feature-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">eco</span></span>
                        <h3 class="feature-title">Eco-Responsable</h3>
                        <p>Réparer plutôt que jeter : nous luttons activement contre l'obsolescence programmée.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CONTACT & CARTE -->
        <section class="section-padding" style="background:var(--color-white);">
            <div class="container fade-in-up">
                <h2 class="section-title">Nous Rendre Visite</h2>
                <div class="contact-grid">
                    <div>
                        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary);">L'Atelier ReparePhone</h3>
                        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start;">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:var(--color-primary); font-size: 2rem;">location_on</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 style="margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Adresse</h4>
                                <p style="color:#555;">65 Route de Blagnac<br>31300 Toulouse<br><span style="font-size:0.85rem; color:#888;">Accès: L1, Bus 70 - Arrêt "Cité Madrid"</span></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start;">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:var(--color-primary); font-size: 2rem;">call</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 style="margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Téléphone</h4>
                                <p style="color:#555;">07 56 91 65 93<br><span style="font-size:0.85rem; color:#888;">Lun-Ven : 9h-19h | Samedi : 10h-18h</span></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; align-items: flex-start;">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:var(--color-primary); font-size: 2rem;">mail</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 style="margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Email</h4>
                                <p style="color:#555;">contact@reparephone-toulouse.fr</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="font-size: 1.1rem; padding: 1rem 2rem;">Prendre RDV en atelier</a>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height: 400px; border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow);">
                        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2888.583307409257!2d1.4172464766861595!3d43.61522205490151!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x12aebaba79fdbb7b%3A0x286d9a9ba47a16f2!2s65%20Rte%20de%20Blagnac%2C%2031200%20Toulouse!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1715481234567!5m2!1sfr!2sfr" width="100%" height="100%" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy"></iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- BEST SELLERS -->
        <section class="section-padding">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title fade-in-up">Nos Appareils Reconditionnés</h2>
                <div class="carousel-wrapper">
                    <div class="product-card fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
                        <span class="badge-etat etat-tb">Très bon état</span>
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1592899677977-9c10ca588bbd?q=80&w=400" alt="iPhone 13" class="product-img">
                        <h3 class="product-title">Apple iPhone 13 - 128 Go</h3>
                        <div class="product-price-wrapper">
                            <span class="price-old">749€</span>
                            <span class="price-new">459€</span>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/devis?model=iPhone%2013" class="btn-primary">Réserver cet appareil</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="product-card fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                        <span class="badge-etat etat-neuf">Comme neuf</span>
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1610945265064-0e34e5519bbf?q=80&w=400" alt="Galaxy S22" class="product-img">
                        <h3 class="product-title">Samsung Galaxy S22 - 256 Go</h3>
                        <div class="product-price-wrapper">
                            <span class="price-old">859€</span>
                            <span class="price-new">389€</span>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/devis?model=Galaxy%20S22" class="btn-primary">Réserver cet appareil</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="product-card fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.3s;">
                        <span class="badge-etat etat-bon">Bon état</span>
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517336714731-489689fd1ca8?q=80&w=400" alt="MacBook Air" class="product-img">
                        <h3 class="product-title">MacBook Air M1 - 256 Go</h3>
                        <div class="product-price-wrapper">
                            <span class="price-old">1199€</span>
                            <span class="price-new">749€</span>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/product?name=MacBook%20Air%20M1&price=749&img=https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517336714731-489689fd1ca8?q=80&w=600" class="btn-primary">Détails & Devis</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="product-card fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.4s;">
                        <span class="badge-etat etat-tb">Très bon état</span>
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585790050230-5dd28404ccb9?q=80&w=400" alt="iPad Air" class="product-img">
                        <h3 class="product-title">Apple iPad Air 4 - 64 Go</h3>
                        <div class="product-price-wrapper">
                            <span class="price-old">669€</span>
                            <span class="price-new">399€</span>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/product?name=iPad%20Air%204&price=399&img=https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585790050230-5dd28404ccb9?q=80&w=600" class="btn-primary">Détails & Devis</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FAQ -->
        <section class="section-padding" id="faq" style="background:var(--color-white);">
            <div class="container fade-in-up">
                <h2 class="section-title">Vos Questions sur la Réparation</h2>
                <div class="faq-accordion">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question">Quelles sont les pannes les plus fréquentes ? <span class="material-symbols-outlined faq-icon">expand_more</span></button>
                        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Écran cassé, remplacement de batterie, connecteur de charge défectueux et désoxydation sont nos interventions quotidiennes.</p></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question">Mes données sont-elles en sécurité ? <span class="material-symbols-outlined faq-icon">expand_more</span></button>
                        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Absolument. Nous n'accédons jamais à vos données personnelles. Cependant, nous recommandons toujours d'effectuer une sauvegarde avant toute réparation par précaution.</p></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question">Proposez-vous un téléphone de prêt ? <span class="material-symbols-outlined faq-icon">expand_more</span></button>
                        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Oui, selon les disponibilités de notre stock, nous pouvons vous prêter un smartphone le temps de l'immobilisation de votre appareil si la réparation dépasse 2 heures.</p></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question">Où est situé votre atelier ? <span class="material-symbols-outlined faq-icon">expand_more</span></button>
